	<![CDATA[
<p> <strong>JA Vintas Template</strong>  for Joomla 2.5 with Virtuemart 2.2.8.</p>

<p>Virtuemart is back in a Fashion shopping template for Joomla 2.5. Go online store with Joomla. JA Vintas has a clean and fresh design in a 
vintage style of color, neat way of presenting products and rich content types.</p>
<p>Smoothly tuning with the latest version of T3 Framework 2.5.4 and Virtuemart 2.2.8, JA Vintas is a powerful shopping template you can choose. 
As an enhancement, latest version of K2 component and Slideshow Lite will perfect the template. Want to open an online store? This is the template 
for you.</p>
<p>Note: JA Vintas does not support RTL language.</p>
